# Certean Monitor - AI Assistant Rules

## MANDATORY: All Code Must Follow These Rules

### Design System Rules

1. **NO ROUNDED CORNERS** - All elements MUST have sharp 90-degree corners
   - Set `border-radius: 0` everywhere
   - Use `border-0` class or explicit `rounded-0`
   - Global CSS enforces: `* { border-radius: 0 !important; }`

2. **NO DROP SHADOWS** - No shadows of any kind
   - Set `box-shadow: none` everywhere
   - Never use `shadow-*` or drop-shadow classes
   - Global CSS enforces: `* { box-shadow: none !important; }`
   - Flat design is mandatory

3. **NO BORDERS ON CARDS** - Cards should NOT have visible borders
   - Always use `border-0` on Card components
   - Use background color contrast (white on light gray) for separation
   - Never use `border` classes on containers

4. **NO FOCUS OUTLINES OR BLUE BORDERS** - No visible focus rings anywhere
   - Set `outline: none` on all interactive elements
   - Never use `focus:ring-*` or `focus:outline-*` classes
   - Global CSS enforces: `*:focus, *:focus-visible, *:focus-within { outline: none !important; box-shadow: none !important; }`
   - Clean, flat interaction states only

5. **CONSISTENT STYLING FROM STUDIO REPO** - Match the Studio design system exactly
   - Source: `/Users/nicolaszander/Desktop/certean/dev/studio`
   - Colors from Studio's globals.css
   - Typography using Geist Sans and Geist Mono fonts

### Page Layout Requirements

Every page MUST use this exact structure:

```tsx
export default function PageName() {
  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen bg-dashboard-view-background p-8">
      <div className="max-w-7xl space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h1 className="text-xl font-bold text-[hsl(var(--dashboard-link-color))]">Title</h1>
          <p className="text-[15px] text-[hsl(var(--dashboard-link-color))] mt-2">Description</p>
        </div>
        {/* Content */}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

