### Color System

- **Page Background:** `bg-dashboard-view-background` (light gray #EEEFF0)
- **Card Background:** `bg-white` (#FFFFFF)
- **Primary Text:** `text-[hsl(var(--dashboard-link-color))]` (greyish-blue)
- **Secondary Text:** `text-gray-500`
- **No Borders:** `border-0` (always)

### Typography

- **Sans Serif:** Geist Sans (via CDN)
- **Monospace:** Geist Mono (via CDN)
- **Numbers/Metrics:** Always use `font-mono` class

### What NOT to Do

❌ **Never use these:**
- `rounded-*` classes (except `rounded-0`)
- `shadow-*` classes (any shadows)
- `drop-shadow-*` classes
- `focus:ring-*` or `focus:outline-*` classes (no focus rings)
- `border` on cards/containers
- `bg-gray-*` for page backgrounds
- Custom colors that don't match the design system
- Round corners anywhere
- Drop shadows anywhere
- Blue focus outlines/borders anywhere

✅ **Always use:**
- `border-0` on all cards
- `bg-dashboard-view-background` for pages
- `bg-white` for cards
- HSL color variables from the design system
- Sharp, clean, professional aesthetic

